  "name": "Set up Maropost Commerce Cloud POS (Point of Sale)",
  "body": "<div><b>Please Note</b>: Maropost Commerce Cloud POS is not available outside of Australia and New Zealand.</div>\n<h3 data-id=\"set-up-pos\">Set up POS</h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FTAb_Dll1cro%3Fwmode%3Dopaque\">https://www.youtube.com/embed/TAb_Dll1cro?wmode=opaque</a></p>\n<hr></hr><h3 data-id=\"pos-settings\">POS Settings</h3>\n<p>Maropost POS comes with a number of built in settings to change functionality of the system. To access these settings in your Maropost Commerce control panel, select <strong>Point of Sale</strong>, and choose <strong>POS Settings</strong>.</p>\n<h4 data-id=\"barcode-scanning\">Barcode Scanning</h4>\n<p>Select which UPC/EAN fields are searched when scanning a barcode in POS.</p>\n<h4 id=\"rounding\" data-id=\"rounding\">Rounding</h4>\n<p>Cash payments rounding mode - Rounding mode to be followed when processing cash transactions</p>\n<p>Cash round to nearest - Nearest rounding value</p>\n<h4 id=\"discounts\" data-id=\"discounts\">Discounts</h4>\n<p>Maximum cashier discount percentage - This is the maximum discount a staff member with cashier permissions can apply to a order</p>\n<p>Maximum store manager discount percentage - This is the maximum discount a staff member with store manager permissions can apply to a order</p>\n<hr></hr><h3 id=\"3\" data-id=\"create-a-pos-desktop-shortcut\">Create a POS Desktop Shortcut</h3>\n<p>Using Maropost POS on a Windows PC? So that you do not need to manually go to <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fpos.neto.com.au\">https://pos.neto.com.au</a> each time you want to access the register through Chrome, you can create a desktop shortcut instead:</p>\n<ol><li>Open Google Chrome</li><li>\n<p>Enter <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fpos.neto.com.au\">https://pos.neto.com.au</a> into the address bar and press <strong>Enter</strong>.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image1\" height=\"439\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/SetupMaropostCommerceCloudPOSPointofSale1.05T5g00000szV55EAE.png\" width=\"700\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 439px; width: 700px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/SetupMaropostCommerceCloudPOSPointofSale1.05T5g00000szV55EAE.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/SetupMaropostCommerceCloudPOSPointofSale1.05T5g00000szV55EAE.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/SetupMaropostCommerceCloudPOSPointofSale1.05T5g00000szV55EAE.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/SetupMaropostCommerceCloudPOSPointofSale1.05T5g00000szV55EAE.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/SetupMaropostCommerceCloudPOSPointofSale1.05T5g00000szV55EAE.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/SetupMaropostCommerceCloudPOSPointofSale1.05T5g00000szV55EAE.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/SetupMaropostCommerceCloudPOSPointofSale1.05T5g00000szV55EAE.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n\t</li><li>\n<p>Navigate to the Chrome menu at the top right of screen.</p>\n\t</li><li>\n<p>Rollover <strong>More Tools</strong> and click <strong>Add To Desktop</strong>.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image2\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/SetupMaropostCommerceCloudPOSPointofSale2.05T5g00000szV6IEAU.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/SetupMaropostCommerceCloudPOSPointofSale2.05T5g00000szV6IEAU.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/SetupMaropostCommerceCloudPOSPointofSale2.05T5g00000szV6IEAU.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/SetupMaropostCommerceCloudPOSPointofSale2.05T5g00000szV6IEAU.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/SetupMaropostCommerceCloudPOSPointofSale2.05T5g00000szV6IEAU.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/SetupMaropostCommerceCloudPOSPointofSale2.05T5g00000szV6IEAU.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/SetupMaropostCommerceCloudPOSPointofSale2.05T5g00000szV6IEAU.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/SetupMaropostCommerceCloudPOSPointofSale2.05T5g00000szV6IEAU.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n\t</li><li>\n<p>A desktop icon for Maropost POS will now be created.</p>\n\t</li><li>\n<p>Return to your desktop and click on this icon to launch Maropost POS.<code class=\"code codeInline\" spellcheck=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\"> </code></p>\n\t</li></ol>",
